        {
            "title": "袁偉豪出動私伙結他自肥向老婆張寶兒上報  陳展鵬唔介意新劇被換角讚張智霖是最合適人選",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"袁偉豪出動私伙結他自肥向老婆張寶兒上報  陳展鵬唔介意新劇被換角讚張智霖是最合適人選\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/52e9c5d39be58b9a8568040050d827b2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051610381230957.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">袁偉豪出動私伙結他自肥向老婆張寶兒上報  陳展鵬唔介意新劇被換角讚張智霖是最合適人選</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>袁偉豪、陳展鵬、譚俊彥等在啟德體藝館舉行的《「保境安民為公益」綜藝大匯演》表演，袁偉豪與譚俊彥搖滾Look夾Band，陳展鵬則表演舞獅。袁偉豪透露帶備了私伙結他演出，笑言有向太太張寶兒上報，是一部中古結他，有時候在網上看到喜歡價錢合適會想買，現在收集了8到10部結他，也喜歡收藏車。\n\n</p><h2>寫了不少新歌交給唱片公司</h2>\n<p>展鵬則指自己沒太多收藏，只是慢慢儲了閱歷，今次舞獅是首次挑戰的表演。至於袁偉豪則與紀錄部隊合作，透露是與消防員夾Band，歌曲也有關。他指早幾日到旺角夾Band玩得很開心，今次演出屬於自肥，因之前在廣州演出表演結他玩得很開心，問可想將演出搬到啟德體藝館？他笑言想，但也要儲歌和需要點時間，他指兒子「袁咕碌」已18個月，出生後他也將時間花在照顧小朋友和音樂上，直言為歌曲減產了劇集，最近寫了不少新歌交給唱片公司。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"譚俊彥等在啟德體藝館舉行的《「保境安民為公益」綜藝大匯演》表演。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5e87789c72e35a576f4dd898dd511b6/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_03_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        譚俊彥等在啟德體藝館舉行的《「保境安民為公益」綜藝大匯演》表演。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"袁偉豪帶備了私伙結他演出，笑言有向太太張寶兒上報。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a5a2816cdf6a1cdc8636934589f41f34/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_12_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        袁偉豪帶備了私伙結他演出，笑言有向太太張寶兒上報。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"袁偉豪與譚俊彥搖滾Look夾Band。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/64f2cba88d24468025d6fabc2ecaf262/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_12_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        袁偉豪與譚俊彥搖滾Look夾Band。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳展鵬則指自己沒太多收藏，只是慢慢儲了閱歷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/291490f9cdafb79f370df7e790b3959c/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_13_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳展鵬則指自己沒太多收藏，只是慢慢儲了閱歷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"袁偉豪現在收集了8到10部結他，也喜歡收藏車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/53a1bc8fde3d4d0e8964d965a97cc694/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_13_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        袁偉豪現在收集了8到10部結他，也喜歡收藏車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"對於新劇被易角，展鵬表示並不知情，笑言公司有好多高層，自己只是「龍虎舞獅」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35be6a3f97f94b0e558d59b8c860f4bf/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_15_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對於新劇被易角，展鵬表示並不知情，笑言公司有好多高層，自己只是「龍虎舞獅」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳展鵬聞「袁咕碌」已18個月時覺得開心，笑言已忘了女兒「小豬比」18個月時的樣子。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f9c95d966c09d7363c9b70e43ea7a859/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_26_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳展鵬聞「袁咕碌」已18個月時覺得開心，笑言已忘了女兒「小豬比」18個月時的樣子。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"3人在台上夾Band。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c8fb6daad22ac7257d1c1614967f063/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_38_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        3人在台上夾Band。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"現場氣氛勁high！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fa9b97625b0703bca6274e6869c42266/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_9_47_38_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場氣氛勁high！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>陳展鵬想生多個</h2>\n<p>陳展鵬聞「袁咕碌」已18個月時覺得開心，笑言已忘了女兒「小豬比」18個月時的樣子，只記得每日都抱住她，問到想再生一胎回味嗎？他笑言想，講出來便有機會，袁偉豪則指生育不是問題，但要花不少時間照顧。談到《璀璨之城》原定由陳展鵬、龔嘉欣及林夏薇演出，最終三人都易角，展鵬表示並不知情，因未到接觸演員的階段，笑言公司有好多高層，自己只是「龍虎舞獅」，也覺得劇集主題是澳門，找到張智霖演是最合適，證明公司有好製作，又有劇集值得追看。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
